high_descs: Move to the tub to left of the sink
Pick up rag from the tub
Move to the shelf to the right of the sink
Place rag on the shelf
Move to the tub to left of the sink
Pick up rag from the tub
Move to the shelf to the right of the sink
Place rag on the shelf
anns.task_desc: Put two rags on the shelf to the right of the sink.

high_descs: Cross the room to stand in front of the bath tub.
Pick up the wash cloth at the right end of the tub, which is closest to the sink.
Carry the wash cloth to stand in front of the towel rack on the wall to the right of the sink.
Place the wash cloth on the cabinet beneath the towel rack.
Turn and move back to the bath tub.
Pick up the rightmost wash cloth of the three that are still there.
Turn and carry the wash cloth to go back and stand in front of the towel rack.
Place the wash cloth on top of the cabinet to the left of the one you previously put there.
anns.task_desc: Move two wash cloths from the tub to the cabinet.

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the right side of the tub.
Pick up the green rag from the tub that's on the right side.
Move to the white shelf that's to the right of the sink.
Place the green rag on the right edge of the white shelf.
Turn around, walk to the tub, and face the tub with the three green rags.
Pick up the green rag from the tub that's all the way to the right.
Turn right and walk to the white shelf with the first green rag on it.
Put the green rag on the white shelf to the left of the first green rag.
anns.task_desc: To move two green rags to the white shelf next to the sink.
